Package: ddst
Title: Data Driven Smooth Tests
Version: 1.5
Authors@R: c(person("Przemyslaw", "Biecek", email = "przemyslaw.biecek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Teresa", "Ledwina", email = "ledwina@impan.pl", role = c("aut")))
Description: Smooth testing of goodness of fit. These tests are data
    driven (alternative hypothesis is dynamically selected based on data). In this
    package you will find various tests for exponent, Gaussian, Gumbel and uniform
    distribution.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 2.7),
    polynom,
    orthopolynom,
    evd
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
